# Heavy site-agent assets — DO NOT ship inside the build context.
# They're bind-mounted at runtime (see docker-compose.yml `volumes:` on the
# frontend service). Keeps the build context slim (~few MB) so Docker BuildKit
# doesn't RPC-EOF on Windows/limited hosts. Linux server: same behavior.
